      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BETTER BANJO (8) boasts a consistent overall record including 31 wins from 92 starts, but missed the frame latest when sixth (22.46) over 390m at Ballarat. Solid record here winning three races. Drawn wide but with a clean break will be tough to beat again. CANYA NITRATE (5) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (30.59) from Box 8 at Angle Park. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Leading player again. AUSSIE SUPREME (2) was out of the placings last time when seventh at this track (16.88) but scored five back at Warragul (22.70). Has a good record here at this journey. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Can measure up this time. FIDDLES (6) was prominent throughout when successful last start. That form reads well.",
